    "This makes the model susceptible to the limitations of individual tools.",
    "In contrast, REFLECTOOL uses multiple tools of the same type to integrate information from diverse sources, thereby improving task performance.",
    "Finally, REFLECTOOL also demonstrates a higher proportion of invoking tools from different categories.",
    "This indicates that REFLEC-TOOL is more flexible in tool usage, being capable of experimenting with a broader range of tools to solve problems.",
    "Although we categorized tools based on the capability dimensions of the model (as shown in Table 9), using tools from other dimensions is not necessarily incorrect."
